{"tid":923404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"土耳其若堅持採購俄S-400 美國防部：將暫停供應F-35","createTime":"2018-12-01T08:25:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T11:55:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b34cee36fb423079071490efde0e790a61fa2b","tid":923404,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpW6fz95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpW6fz95.jpg&h=264c4a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國防部報告指出，若土耳其不放棄向俄國採購S-400防空系統，美國將停止F-35戰機的供應。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n2018-12-01 15:31<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕土耳其去年向俄國簽署採購4套S-400防空系統的協議，不但引起北約擔憂，也讓美國感到相當不滿。有外媒報導，11月初由美國國防部提交至美國國會的最新報告顯示，若土耳其不放棄對S-400的採購，美國將把土耳其排除出F-35戰機的生產項目。<br />\n<br />\n《俄羅斯衛星通訊社》報導，美國防部於11月初提交美國國會的報告指出，「如果土耳其不放棄購買S-400防空系統，將重新考慮土耳其作為8個夥伴國之一，繼續參與F-35戰機生產項目的問題」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，從2002年起，土耳其參與美國領導的F-35戰機多國研發項目，並有意購買至少100架F-35戰機。日前，由於土耳其向俄國採購總價達25億美元的S-400防空系統，並預計於明年開始供貨，迫使美國國會警告，可能會暫停向土耳其供應F-35戰機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2629827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2629827&d=6QdQly7TZhMNNtULIaCvDl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=13359caf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2629827&h=256de0f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2629827</a>"},{"pid":"5735ce684b6b88b4cec97d5a3873cd7ca6b542f3","tid":923404,"uid":75072,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"土耳其伊斯撚真係好唔可靠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccea9ebf0d56a986624e7d11bd0cc94566f68944","tid":923404,"uid":5267,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24d4b0fd156bed334e14a640c7ac